---
---
<section id="reviews" class="section section-alt">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <div class="testimonial-head text-center">
      <div class="head-top" style="justify-content: center;">
        <span class="section-num">/ 05</span>
        <span class="section-kicker">What Customers Say</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Real Words.<br/>Real Yards.</h2>
    </div>
    <blockquote class="testimonial">
      <div class="testimonial-marks">"</div>
      <p class="testimonial-quote">Noah came out to quote, mow our yard &amp; haul some dirt/grass away all in the same day. We have almost half an acre so it was a big job &amp; he tackled it like it was nothing! Awesome kid who is a hard worker &amp; very respectful. You won't be disappointed in his work!</p>
      <footer class="testimonial-author">
        <div class="testimonial-avatar">CG</div>
        <div>
          <div class="testimonial-name">Chloe Garcia</div>
          <div class="testimonial-meta">South Bend customer · via Facebook</div>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </blockquote>
    <div class="testimonial-links">
      <a href="https://www.facebook.com/people/Fernandezs-landscaping/61574590599260/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">More reviews on Facebook</a>
      <span class="dot">•</span>
      <a href="https://www.yelp.com/biz/fernandez-landscaping-south-bend" target="_blank" rel="noopener">See us on Yelp</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonial-head {
    margin-bottom: 56px;
  }
  .head-top {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .head-top .section-kicker { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .testimonial {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--white);
    padding: 56px 48px 40px;
    border-radius: 0;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--charcoal);
    box-shadow: 8px 8px 0 var(--forest);
  }
  .testimonial-marks {
    position: absolute;
    top: 8px;
    left: 28px;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 7rem;
    color: var(--lime);
    line-height: 1;
    opacity: 0.4;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .testimonial-quote {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 1.9vw, 1.55rem);
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }
  .testimonial-author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .testimonial-avatar {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    background: var(--forest);
    color: var(--bone);
    border-radius: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }
  .testimonial-name {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    font-size: 1.02rem;
  }
  .testimonial-meta {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--gray);
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .testimonial-links {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 32px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--gray);
  }
  .testimonial-links a {
    color: var(--forest);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .testimonial-links .dot {
    margin: 0 10px;
    color: var(--gray-light);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .testimonial {
      padding: 48px 24px 32px;
      box-shadow: 5px 5px 0 var(--forest);
    }
    .testimonial-marks { left: 16px; font-size: 4.5rem; }
    .testimonial-quote { text-align: center; }
    .testimonial-author { justify-content: center; }
  }
</style>
